---
const mainImage = {
  webp: "/images/historia.webp",
  png: "/images/historia.png",
  alt: "img-historia",
};
---

<section
  class="w-full py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-50/30 to-white relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/4 left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200/10 to-orange-200/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-10 w-48 h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-300/8 to-yellow-300/8 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Enhanced Title Section -->
    <div
      class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="800"
    >
      <!-- Decorative pattern -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div
          class="hidden sm:block w-16 lg:w-24 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-amber-400 to-amber-600"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-600 rounded-full transform rotate-45">
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-20 lg:w-32 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-400"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-600 rounded-full transform rotate-45">
        </div>
        <div
          class="hidden sm:block w-16 lg:w-24 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 via-amber-400 to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main title -->
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-amber-900 tracking-widest mb-4"
      >
        CONÓCENOS
      </h2>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p
        class="text-lg md:text-xl text-amber-700/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium"
      >
        Descubre la historia detrás de nuestros quesos artesanales
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content container -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center max-w-7xl mx-auto"
    >
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div
        class="order-2 lg:order-1"
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-duration="800"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-lg border border-amber-100/50"
        >
          <!-- Section title -->
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h3
              class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-amber-900 mb-4 tracking-wide"
            >
              Nuestra Historia
            </h3>

            <!-- Decorative line -->
            <div
              class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-500 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"
            >
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story content -->
          <div class="space-y-6 text-amber-900/90">
            <!-- Year badge and first paragraph -->
            <div class="relative">
              <div
                class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-16 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-500 rounded-r-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
              >
                <span class="text-black text-base font-bold">1998</span>
              </div>

              <p
                class="text-lg text-black/85 md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-justify pl-16"
              >
                En el corazón de los Andes peruanos, nació nuestra asociación de
                productores de queso "Don Lucio" en 1998. Todo comenzó cuando un
                grupo de familias ganaderas decidió unir fuerzas para preservar
                las técnicas tradicionales de elaboración de quesos artesanales.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Separator -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2">
              <div
                class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-amber-300 to-transparent"
              >
              </div>
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <div
                class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-amber-300 to-transparent"
              >
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Second paragraph with quote styling -->
            <div class="relative">
              <p
                class="text-lg md:text-xl text-black/75 leading-relaxed text-justify pl-8 pr-4"
              >
                Don Lucio Mamani, fundador y maestro quesero, transmitió su
                pasión y conocimientos a toda una generación de productores
                locales. Su visión de crear productos de calidad, respetando las
                tradiciones y aprovechando la rica leche de las alturas, sentó
                las bases de lo que hoy es nuestra asociación.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Founder signature -->
            <div class="text-right pt-4">
              <p class="text-amber-700 font-semibold text-lg">— Don Lucio</p>
              <p class="text-amber-600 text-sm">Fundador y Maestro Quesero</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Content -->
      <div
        class="order-1 lg:order-2"
        data-aos="fade-left"
        data-aos-duration="800"
        data-aos-delay="400"
      >
        <div class="relative group">
          <!-- Decorative frame -->
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/20 via-orange-400/10 to-yellow-400/20 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-60"
          >
          </div>

          <!-- Main image container -->
          <div class="relative bg-white p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
            <div class="block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src={mainImage.webp}
                alt={mainImage.alt}
                class="w-full h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] object-cover transition-all duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
                onerror={`this.onerror=null; this.src='${mainImage.png}';`}
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
